  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Manage a team of sales executive to achieve company objectives and targets.</li><li>Sales development for Industrial products.</li><li>Regular customer engagement to get customer information, competitive trend, explore new sales opportunities and maintain good relationship.</li><li>Create business plan and setting of personal targets to meet company KPIs.</li><li>Budget and allocate resources and expenses.</li><li>Submit monthly sales report and project updates.</li><li>Handling customer complaints and addressing customer issues.</li><li>Ad-hoc support on delivery, collection, returns, and customer related issues.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Knowledge of Energy & Industrial related products.</li><li>Strong market development & product introduction abilities.</li><li>Good negotiation & communication skills.</li><li>Dedication with strong responsibilities, and able to take up new challenges.</li><li>Ability to work under pressure.</li><li>2 to 3 years of sales experience in the related Industry.</li><li>Sales in other Industry may be considered with proven track record</li><li>Proficient in spoken and written Japanese.</li></ul>",
